## Google Gemini
# Get from Google AI Studio → API key
GOOGLE_API_KEY=your_google_api_key_here

## ElevenLabs
# Get from ElevenLabs dashboard → API key + voice ID
ELEVENLABS_API_KEY=your_elevenlabs_key_here
